== 相關法律與管制 ==
根據WHO調查指出，電子菸在不同國家規範不同，包含藥品、菸品、一般消費品等。電子菸的發展可能關係到[[菸草|菸草]]的法律和醫療藥品政策，對許多國家相對新穎、以及相關使用公眾健康問題，電子菸現行法規與一般輿論見解與社會觀感在各地有很大的不同。在2014年2月，[[歐洲議會|歐洲議會]]通過了要求標準化和質量控制液體和霧化器，標示液體成分，以及保護兒童打樣和防篡改液體包裝規定。在2014年4月[[美國食品藥品監督管理局|美國食品藥品監督管理局]]公布了電子煙按照類似的思路擬議規例。2021年5月，[[世界衛生組織|世界衛生組織]](WHO)發表WHO study group on tobacco product regulation報告，對電子煙提出各國在管理辦法上的方向建議 <ref>[https://www.who.int/publications/i/item/9789240022720 WHO study group on tobacco product regulation: Report on the scientific basis of tobacco product regulation: eighth report of a WHO study group.] {{Wayback|url=https://www.who.int/publications/i/item/9789240022720 |date=20210707080413 }} 4 May 2021.</ref>。

* {{英國}}：電子菸被獨立定義，並需於The Medicines and Healthcare Products Regulatory Agency (MHRA)註冊方可販售 <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.gov.uk/guidance/e-cigarettes-regulations-for-consumer-products|title=E-cigarettes: regulations for consumer products|website=GOV.UK|access-date=2021-06-16|archive-date=2021-11-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211127202436/https://www.gov.uk/guidance/e-cigarettes-regulations-for-consumer-products|dead-url=no}}</ref>。電子菸目前採三軌制，尼古丁電子菸分醫療用及一般使用，非尼古丁電子菸屬一般消費產品 <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/e-cigarettes-and-heated-tobacco-products-evidence-review/evidence-review-of-e-cigarettes-and-heated-tobacco-products-2018-executive-summary|title=Evidence review of e-cigarettes and heated tobacco products 2018: executive summary|website=GOV.UK|access-date=2018-05-04|archive-date=2021-05-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210513102123/https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/e-cigarettes-and-heated-tobacco-products-evidence-review/evidence-review-of-e-cigarettes-and-heated-tobacco-products-2018-executive-summary|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/e-cigarettes-and-vaping-policy-regulation-and-guidance|title=E-cigarettes and vaping: policy, regulation and guidance|publisher=|access-date=2018-05-04|archive-date=2021-03-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210319143943/https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/e-cigarettes-and-vaping-policy-regulation-and-guidance|dead-url=no}}</ref>。英國政府以法律來管理電子菸行銷方式、尼古丁容量、菸油裝填容量，且電子菸的製造商、進口商與分銷商皆須遵守規範。英國公共衛生部(PHE) 在2021年2月發表電子菸霧化器的第七份報告Vaping in England: evidence update February 2021，該報告總結了使用電子菸霧化產品的證據，以作為政策和法規提供依據。英國制定2030年無菸目標，制定新的菸草控制計劃並審查 Tobacco and Related Products Regulations (TRPR)，為審查所有霧化法規（以及其他尼古丁和煙草），法規提供了機會，以確保這些法規適用並幫助吸煙者戒菸，同時管理從未吸煙者的攝取風險<ref>{{cite web|last1=McNeill|first1=A|last2=Brose|first2=LS|last3=Calder|first3=R|last4=Simonavicius|first4=E|last5=Robson|first5=D|url=https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/vaping-in-england-evidence-update-february-2021/vaping-in-england-2021-evidence-update-summary|title=Vaping in England: 2021 evidence update summary|location=UK|publisher=Public Health England|date=23 February 2021|access-date=2021-06-16|archive-date=2021-12-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211222080839/https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/vaping-in-england-evidence-update-february-2021/vaping-in-england-2021-evidence-update-summary|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

* {{美國}}：[[美國食品和藥物管理局|美國食品和藥物管理局]]（FDA）將電子菸定義為菸品<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.fda.gov/tobacco-products/products-ingredients-components/vaporizers-e-cigarettes-and-other-electronic-nicotine-delivery-systems-ends|title=Vaporizers, E-Cigarettes, and other Electronic Nicotine Delivery Systems (ENDS)|website=fda.gov|access-date=2021-06-16|archive-date=2021-11-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211125125153/https://www.fda.gov/tobacco-products/products-ingredients-components/vaporizers-e-cigarettes-and-other-electronic-nicotine-delivery-systems-ends|dead-url=no}}</ref>，除非銷售時將其定義為藥用或醫療產品。[[美国联邦航空管理局|美国联邦航空管理局]]（FAA）2015年初以消防安全為理由向航空公司發安全警報，{{Link-en|行李|Checked baggage}}內禁止有電子菸。雖然可以手提攜帶電子菸，但是飛行途中禁食電子菸<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/blogs/dr-gridlock/wp/2015/01/26/the-faa-wants-you-to-carry-on-your-e-cigs/|title=The FAA wants you to carry on your e-Cigs|author=Ashley Hasley III|work=[[The_Washington_Post|The Washington Post]]|date=26 January 2015|accessdate=2018-10-10|archive-date=2015-08-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150814185857/http://www.washingtonpost.com/blogs/dr-gridlock/wp/2015/01/26/the-faa-wants-you-to-carry-on-your-e-cigs/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。美國紐約則從2020年7月起禁止銷售香味電子菸<ref>{{cite web|url=https://apnews.com/article/0236aee907924aa4a3a0ee0f5fb18384|title=New York City lawmakers vote to ban flavored vaping products|date=2019-11-23|website=AP NEWS|access-date=2021-06-16|archive-date=2021-06-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210627210101/https://apnews.com/article/0236aee907924aa4a3a0ee0f5fb18384|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=New York City lawmakers vote to ban flavored vaping products|url=https://www.seattletimes.com/seattle-news/health/new-york-city-lawmakers-vote-to-ban-flavored-vaping-products/|access-date=2021-06-03|date=2019-11-26|work=The Seattle Times|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-06-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210604062331/https://www.seattletimes.com/seattle-news/health/new-york-city-lawmakers-vote-to-ban-flavored-vaping-products/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。美國[[耶魯大學|耶魯大學]]公共衛生學院研究人員亦於2021年5月在[[美國醫學會雜誌|美國醫學會雜誌]]（the Journal of the American Medical Association）發表一篇使用[[美國疾病管制與預防中心|美國疾病管制與預防中心]](CDC) 2011-2019 年青年風險行為監測系統 (YRBSS) 兩年一次的學區調查數據，分析 100,695 名未成年者的吸煙情況。該研究發現，與其他學區相比，舊金山的加味菸禁令明顯提高了當地未成年者的吸煙率，主因為電子菸使用者使用加味菸的比例更高，而在口味遭到限制後，多數人即轉為使用[[香菸|紙菸]]。該研究也表示若監管機構針對加味菸實施禁令，反而會導致某些族群的吸菸率增加，而不會如預期般的有效降低電子菸使用率 <ref>{{cite web|last1=Friedman|first1=Abigail S|url=https://jamanetwork.com/journals/jamapediatrics/fullarticle/2780248?guestAccessKey=fc999fc8-50ed-46f0-b91f-5e425bf79e33&utm_source=For_The_Media&utm_medium=referral&utm_campaign=ftm_links&utm_content=tfl&utm_term=052421|title=A Difference-in-Differences Analysis of Youth Smoking and a Ban on Sales of Flavored Tobacco Products in San Francisco, California|location=US|publisher=JAMA Pediatr|date=24 May 2021|access-date=2021-06-16|archive-date=2021-08-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210818061523/https://jamanetwork.com/journals/jamapediatrics/fullarticle/2780248?guestAccessKey=fc999fc8-50ed-46f0-b91f-5e425bf79e33&utm_source=For_The_Media&utm_medium=referral&utm_campaign=ftm_links&utm_content=tfl&utm_term=052421|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2021年10月FDA首度准售Vuse Solo電子煙，部分原因為菸草味電子煙能減少紙菸使用量，對青少年也不具吸引力，與紙菸相比有相當程度的「減害」<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.fda.gov/news-events/press-announcements/fda-grants-first-ever-modified-risk-orders-eight-smokeless-tobacco-products?fbclid=IwAR275z3-0b0TxXy63e2KQSqT6B8o4DsLo0Zk5xvORdUJh4e27JpDquzraKo|title=FDA grants first-ever modified risk orders to eight smokeless tobacco products|publisher=|access-date=2021-11-10|archive-date=2021-11-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211110092307/https://www.fda.gov/news-events/press-announcements/fda-grants-first-ever-modified-risk-orders-eight-smokeless-tobacco-products?fbclid=IwAR275z3-0b0TxXy63e2KQSqT6B8o4DsLo0Zk5xvORdUJh4e27JpDquzraKo|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

* {{紐西蘭}}政府針對電子菸目前採一般消費品管理：非含尼古丁電子菸油，皆為一般消費品，2018年元月分推動[[香菸|紙菸]]環境汙染，立法禁止販售，尼古丁則屬第三類管制藥品，一般民眾禁止持有 <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.health.govt.nz/our-work/preventative-health-wellness/tobacco-control/vaping-e-cigarettes|title=Ministry of Health position statement – Vaping products|publisher=|access-date=2018-05-04|archive-date=2018-05-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180505070048/https://www.health.govt.nz/our-work/preventative-health-wellness/tobacco-control/vaping-e-cigarettes|dead-url=no}}</ref>。紐西蘭設立2025年無煙國家目標後，於2020年11月11日生效 Smokefree Environments and Regulated Products (Vaping) Amendment Act；該法案確保向希望使用危害較小的替代品的吸煙者提供電子菸霧化產品，並確保不將這些產品銷售或出售給年輕人<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.health.govt.nz/our-work/regulation-health-and-disability-system/regulation-vaping-and-smokeless-tobacco-products/about-smokefree-environments-and-regulated-products-vaping-amendment-act|title=About the Smokefree Environments and Regulated Products (Vaping) Amendment Act|website=health.govt.nz/|access-date=2021-06-16|archive-date=2021-11-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211123161409/https://www.health.govt.nz/our-work/regulation-health-and-disability-system/regulation-vaping-and-smokeless-tobacco-products/about-smokefree-environments-and-regulated-products-vaping-amendment-act|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

